snippet.title: Newlyweds Happy Couple Family Simulator -Gameplay #1
snippet.description:
Newlyweds Happy Couple Family Simulator - Gameplay #1

⏭️Google Play Link - https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...

⏭️ABOUT THIS GAMES

Time to prepare for your wedding, in this amazing family simulator

For those who loved playing family games, this is a treat to play Newlyweds Happy Couple Family Simulator. You’ve carried your love story a long way now. It’s time to get married this summer. Let’s play the role of a happy couple soon to be married. You own a house in middle of city. You’ve spend quite a time as bachelor so finally you decide to marry your girlfriend. Buy your girlfriend expensive presents and take her out for a party. Spend life with your love and let’s build a family.


The game begins with your life in middle of a time when you are planning to get married and start a newlywed life. Newlyweds Happy Couple is a best family simulator game where you will get married. Your closing in to the big wedding day of your life. Go and buy the wedding ring to propose your girlfriend and ask her if she will marry you. The wedding day is near and you want a perfect wedding day ahead. Go buy the wedding dress for you and your loved one. Begin your new life with your housewife as the newlywed happy couple. A best family game for those who want to experience the newlywed life. 

Time to have some adventure when you feel blessed with a Housewife. Play both roles a husband and a loving wife.
